{"tid":2530492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平視察問群眾「怎知我來了？」網神回：被安排來的嘛","createTime":"2021-05-14T12:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T18:58:16.000Z","uid":32511,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ba563930fd5f70d26f3ef08572e56b19591aeab6","tid":2530492,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T12:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/05/14/phpVmMd4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F05%2F14%2FphpVmMd4O.jpg&h=0a1aed67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=758570901472262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D758570901472262&d=z1Z9%2FhyuGVbDXJZ%2FGqhOoUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=75a86545\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=758570901472262</a><br />\n<br />\n中國領導人習近平持續視察行程，他近日到訪河南省，看見現場已有大批群眾等待，竟問：「你們怎麼知道我來了啊？」群眾回答：「當然知道了。」影片曝光後網友神回：「被安排來的嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n根據《自由亞洲電台》報導，中共總書記習近平週三（12日）視察河南南陽，途經南陽月季博覽園，現場有大量「群眾」歡欣鼓舞地喊著「歡迎來」，習近平見狀竟問：「你們怎麼知道我來了？」「群眾」回答「當然知道了。」習近平又問：「你們是諸葛亮啊？」<br />\n<br />\n「群眾」接著七嘴八舌地說：「是來採風（取景）的」，聲稱「搞攝影」，不過習近平接著問：「沒照相機啊？」一群人又回答：「滑手機拍的！」接著習近平在「群眾」注目禮下離開現場。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友見到這段影片，紛紛留言諷刺「因為有傀儡安排假觀眾」、「好像老師與學生，有問有答」、「是人都知道全部都是特約演員」、「三百包飯盒已經準備好了」、「哈哈，當然是心電感應啦，不會做假」、「出來宣傳如果沒人知道那宣傳做的很失敗」、「聽他說話，越來越像毛新宇」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3532518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3532518&d=z1Z9%2FhyuGVbDXJZ%2FGqhOoUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=fc95fe20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3532518&h=12c19ddb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3532518</a>"},{"pid":"bbc336cf6ff7e409f448aa32e2b7ba55c5b7736c","tid":2530492,"uid":254594,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy